talking to him again.

30:37.210 --> 30:39.270
Pinocchio!

31:18.690 --> 31:22.420
It's finished.
Isn't it beautiful?

31:22.590 --> 31:24.390
Everything you bake
is beautiful, dear.

31:24.560 --> 31:27.460
You know, I sold it to
the magistrate by the pound,

31:27.630 --> 31:30.760
and the best part is,
l cheated on the weight.

31:30.930 --> 31:33.430
You're very good at that, dear.

31:38.240 --> 31:43.110
It reminds me of the cake
that we had on our wedding day.

31:58.430 --> 32:00.790
Don't eat that.

32:00.960 --> 32:02.230
- I'm not eating anything.
- Not you!

32:02.400 --> 32:04.300
Look!

32:07.800 --> 32:10.030
Mmm, more?

32:10.210 --> 32:11.500
I'll give you more.

32:11.670 --> 32:14.170
You're a bad boy, huh?

32:14.340 --> 32:16.740
Real bad boy.

32:21.750 --> 32:24.720
Little mischief maker.

32:47.410 --> 32:50.110
Your father's going to
pay for this!

33:00.290 --> 33:01.780
Got him.

33:05.260 --> 33:06.730
Even better.

33:23.210 --> 33:24.240
Pinocchio.

33:25.010 --> 33:27.380
Papa, want some?

33:27.550 --> 33:30.250
Geppetto, he's yours?

33:30.420 --> 33:32.080
Arrest him.

33:32.260 --> 33:33.720
Arrest both of them.

33:33.890 --> 33:34.880
You're under arrest, signore.

33:35.060 --> 33:36.220
Wait.

33:36.390 --> 33:37.590
Papa.

33:37.760 --> 33:39.590
Come on. you, too, little one.

33:41.500 --> 33:43.400
Hey, stop him!

33:43.570 --> 33:45.330
There goes our commission.

33:45.500 --> 33:46.990
Au contraire.

33:47.170 --> 33:49.760
I have a feeling our job
just got easier.

34:13.600 --> 34:15.000
Come on, now.

34:15.159 --> 34:17.130
It's past your bedtime.
Into bed.

34:17.300 --> 34:18.790
Good night, son.

34:20.800 --> 34:23.639
I love you, Papa.

34:27.409 --> 34:29.380
I love you, Papa.

35:34.640 --> 35:36.700
I can't do anything right.

35:36.880 --> 35:38.240
The human dilemma.

35:38.410 --> 35:39.970
Who said that?

35:40.150 --> 35:41.240
Or is it the puppet dilemma?

35:41.420 --> 35:43.610
You've still got cake
on your face.

35:46.520 --> 35:47.890
What?

35:49.590 --> 35:51.220
Say, do you always
squish someone...

35:51.390 --> 35:53.330
before being
formally introduced?

35:53.500 --> 35:56.950
Are--are you a termite?

35:57.130 --> 35:58.830
Oh, please!

35:59.000 --> 36:01.100
So you're not going to eat me.

36:01.270 --> 36:03.300
Thanks for the offer,
but I'm on a low-wood diet.

36:04.070 --> 36:06.100
Let me introduce myself.

36:06.280 --> 36:10.000
The name is...
Pugnacio Elecuzio P. Elegante.

