36:22.000 --> 36:22.420
Pepe.

36:23.760 --> 36:25.590
- Pepe?
- You don't like it?

36:25.760 --> 36:27.630
- It's OK.
- I'm very sensitive, you know.

36:27.800 --> 36:29.130
No. It's--it's fine.

36:29.300 --> 36:31.790
We can't all
be called Pinocchio.

36:31.970 --> 36:32.990
Now listen to me.

36:33.170 --> 36:36.760
I'm here because you are
one tumult little puppet.

36:36.940 --> 36:39.910
Your papa's in jail,
you're all alone,

36:40.080 --> 36:41.940
you trounced me
in the alley,

36:42.110 --> 36:45.980
and I'm here to see that we get
our friendship back on track...

36:46.150 --> 36:47.510
right this very second!

36:49.120 --> 36:51.280
Sorry.
Didn't meant to holler,

36:51.450 --> 36:52.850
but insects are people,
too, you know?

36:53.020 --> 36:57.290
And I'm a lot more than your
standard garden-variety cricket.

36:57.460 --> 36:58.950
I'm a teller of truths.

36:59.960 --> 37:02.760
I'll be your best friend,
pine cone.

37:02.930 --> 37:04.490
I'll open your eyes.

37:04.670 --> 37:07.160
I'm not a pine cone.
I'm a boy.

37:07.340 --> 37:09.700
Not yet, but it's
a top-notch goal...

37:09.870 --> 37:12.240
for such a cute little puppet,

37:12.410 --> 37:14.000
which is why it's time
to get to work.

37:14.180 --> 37:17.310
You can become a real boy
one you get the tools.

37:17.480 --> 37:20.570
I'll advise you
and be your regal guardian,

37:20.750 --> 37:22.310
but you've got to do
the hard work.

37:22.490 --> 37:23.820
You, my little sapling,

37:23.990 --> 37:25.820
will have to shed something blood,
sweat, and tree bark.

37:25.990 --> 37:28.050
Total eclipse.

37:30.030 --> 37:32.390
Visitors. How wonderful.

37:32.560 --> 37:35.530
Get the door, and be polite,
and smile, now.

37:35.700 --> 37:38.390
Show those pearly whites.

37:43.810 --> 37:45.640
No, stop.

37:45.810 --> 37:47.000
- Let me go.
- Come on. We've got you now.

37:59.820 --> 38:02.590
Court is now in session.

38:02.760 --> 38:07.130
Case number 491, your honor.

38:07.300 --> 38:14.000
The People versus Luca Antonio
Renaldo Geppetto Baldini.

38:14.170 --> 38:16.930
My papa.

38:17.110 --> 38:18.840
It will be all right, Pinocchio.

38:19.010 --> 38:22.210
There he is, your honor,
the little mutilator.

38:22.380 --> 38:23.940
He ruined my cannolis.

38:24.110 --> 38:25.440
He ruined my fruit tarts.

38:25.620 --> 38:26.640
Silence, woman.

38:26.820 --> 38:29.340
He even ruined my grandmother's
torta della nonna...

38:29.520 --> 38:31.780
with the pinoli
and the chocolate--

38:31.950 --> 38:32.780
Are you done?

38:32.960 --> 38:35.220
No, I am not done. I would--

38:35.390 --> 38:36.980
Arrest her!

38:37.160 --> 38:38.750
Now I'm done.

38:42.970 --> 38:44.560
Now...

38:44.730 --> 38:46.600
Since you, Geppetto,

38:46.770 --> 38:51.230
are responsible
for this, uh, puppet,

38:51.410 --> 38:53.340
how do you plead?

38:53.510 --> 38:55.370
Guilty, sir.

38:57.650 --> 39:02.410
You will pay 20,000 lira
to the bakers...

39:02.590 --> 39:04.490
and 10,000 to the court.

39:04.650 --> 39:05.590
l--l don't have it.

39:05.760 --> 39:07.520
That--that's
three years' wages.

39:07.690 --> 39:11.520
If you cannot pay, then you
will go to debtors prison.

39:11.690 --> 39:14.160
Three years locked away.

39:16.170 --> 39:17.360
Your honor.

39:19.800 --> 39:24.640
I propose the court
allow me to pay the fines...

39:24.810 --> 39:28.140
for this poor,
impoverished peasant.

39:28.310 --> 39:31.440
This is most generous
of you, Signore Lorenzini.

39:31.610 --> 39:33.510
Kindness is my weakness.

39:33.680 --> 39:37.950
Of course, no good deed
should go without obligation,

39:38.120 --> 39:42.580
so all I ask is to keep
Pinocchio in return.

39:42.760 --> 39:45.850
Lorenzini, please,
take any other puppet.

39:46.030 --> 39:49.620
I will work for you day
and night the rest of my life.

39:49.800 --> 39:56.670
Geppetto, is it just
money for you?

39:56.840 --> 39:58.570
Pinocchio needs a home.

39:58.740 --> 40:01.610
All you can offer him...

40:01.780 --> 40:05.580
is table scarps
and cold winter nights,

40:05.750 --> 40:08.650
but with me,
he will have a family.

40:08.820 --> 40:11.910
What's a family, Papa?

40:12.090 --> 40:16.180
My goodness,
such a heartbreaking question,

40:16.360 --> 40:19.490
one no one should
ever have to ask.

40:19.660 --> 40:23.360
Pinocchio, I can
give you a life...

40:23.530 --> 40:27.090
other little boys
only dream of.

40:27.270 --> 40:30.430
What is your decision, Geppetto?

40:48.760 --> 40:50.120
Listen to me.

40:50.290 --> 40:55.360
You're going to go
with that man now.

40:55.530 --> 40:58.690
But I want to be with you.

40:58.870 --> 40:59.990
I know,

41:00.170 --> 41:04.700
but you see--you see,
there--there's no other choice.

41:04.870 --> 41:06.310
You're my papa.

41:06.480 --> 41:08.340
I can't be your papa.

41:08.510 --> 41:11.140
You're made of wood.

41:11.310 --> 41:13.250
You're not flesh.
You're not a real boy.

41:14.720 --> 41:16.450
Now go, for everyone's good!

41:23.890 --> 41:26.730
Let's go.

41:26.900 --> 41:28.230
Son.

41:50.350 --> 41:52.180
Good boy.

42:02.400 --> 42:04.330
I love you, Papa.

42:21.150 --> 42:22.950
I'm sorry.

42:26.460 --> 42:30.390
Why does everything good
get thrown to the beasts?

