Champagne.

45:10.490 --> 45:13.080
OK, kiddo, now we're
in the swing of things.

45:13.260 --> 45:16.020
Lesson number one--
beware of temptation.

45:16.190 --> 45:18.350
Applause may be good
for the moment,

45:18.530 --> 45:20.150
but love is everlasting.

45:20.330 --> 45:22.920
I do have love.
Lorenzini loves me.

45:23.100 --> 45:25.570
That's not love.
He's fooling you.

45:25.730 --> 45:27.430
He's got evil plans
in the works,

45:27.600 --> 45:29.470
and he's using you
to make them come true.

45:29.640 --> 45:32.400
Why do you have to
make everything so hard?

45:32.580 --> 45:33.970
No pain, no gain.

45:35.780 --> 45:38.270
They love us.

45:38.450 --> 45:40.420
To success.

45:44.020 --> 45:47.480
Wait till they see
what I've got for them next.

