ls it hot in here,
or is it me? Ciao!

48:18.070 --> 48:21.770
Come here, you little--

48:36.760 --> 48:37.820
There.

48:39.160 --> 48:40.320
Get him.

48:40.500 --> 48:41.330
Signor Lorenzini,

48:41.500 --> 48:43.930
I'm sorry things
didn't quite work out.

48:44.100 --> 48:46.530
I don't know. I think things
turned out rather well.

48:46.700 --> 48:48.800
I guess you'll pay us
our commission now, huh?

48:48.970 --> 48:50.960
Pay you?

48:51.140 --> 48:54.670
I will kill you if you don't
bring me that puppet.

48:59.280 --> 49:01.770
I thought you were burned.

49:05.190 --> 49:06.680
Where's my Pinocchio?

49:17.630 --> 49:20.120
There he is! On the bridge!

49:22.200 --> 49:23.730
Grab him!

49:28.380 --> 49:31.840
@ What are we made of?

49:32.010 --> 49:34.950
@ Just for this moment

49:35.120 --> 49:38.710
@ Take your life
into your hands

49:38.890 --> 49:43.190
@ You'll decide
what you are made of

49:43.360 --> 49:47.120
@ What it is that I can be

49:47.300 --> 49:50.090
@ Turn around

49:50.270 --> 49:53.360
@ Think again

50:11.220 --> 50:13.120
Pinocchio?

50:15.720 --> 50:17.390
Oh, Leona

50:17.660 --> 50:18.850
I've been all over town.

50:19.030 --> 50:20.930
So have l.
l hope you had more luck.

50:21.100 --> 50:22.590
I asked Carmella
if she'd seen Pinocchio.

50:22.760 --> 50:24.100
She said no.

50:24.270 --> 50:25.390
But then I went to see Tino.

50:25.570 --> 50:26.690
He said no.

50:26.870 --> 50:28.500
But then I went to see
Maria, the witch--

50:28.670 --> 50:30.300
the one who hasn't
spoken in years.

50:30.470 --> 50:32.700
- What did she say?
- Nothing.

50:32.880 --> 50:35.970
But... she gave me this.

50:36.140 --> 50:37.200
A stick?

50:37.380 --> 50:38.900
What's it mean?

50:39.080 --> 50:40.640
Think about it.

50:40.820 --> 50:43.050
Pinocchio probably feels like
he can't come home,

50:43.220 --> 50:44.910
like he'd only be
in trouble if he does.

50:45.090 --> 50:45.920
Yes...

50:46.090 --> 50:50.120
Where would you go
if you felt that way?

50:50.290 --> 50:52.660
l... don't know.

50:53.960 --> 50:56.290
Someplace safe.

50:56.470 --> 50:58.300
And where would that be,

50:58.470 --> 51:00.800
given the fact that
you're made out of wood?

51:03.110 --> 51:04.870
The forest.

51:05.040 --> 51:07.130
Thank you, Maria.

51:07.310 --> 51:09.640
What are you waiting for?
Let's go.

51:22.190 --> 51:24.250
Smell that pine.

51:24.430 --> 51:26.220
You know, they ought
to bottle that scent...

51:26.400 --> 51:28.260
so you can spray it
around your house.

51:28.430 --> 51:31.870
Have I told you what an honor
it is to be your cricket?

51:32.030 --> 51:35.090
You were brilliant last night.

51:35.270 --> 51:37.670
You stayed cool
when things got hot.

51:37.840 --> 51:40.870
You did the right thing,
and you deserve to be proud.

51:41.040 --> 51:42.700
This is where I belong.

51:42.880 --> 51:45.970
You know, I prefer
the beach myself,

51:46.150 --> 51:48.340
but property there
is so expensive.

51:54.490 --> 51:57.690
You've gone back to your roots.

51:57.860 --> 51:59.990
I know you feel lost, Pinocchio.

52:00.160 --> 52:05.120
Believe me, it's only natural,
but you can't stay here.

52:05.300 --> 52:06.700
Go away, please.

52:06.870 --> 52:09.130
I fell happy here.

52:09.300 --> 52:11.430
You can't sleep
your problems away.

52:11.610 --> 52:13.130
You've got to get back
to your papa.

52:13.310 --> 52:14.300
Bye.

52:14.480 --> 52:16.940
We've got to roll.
Let's make tracks. Let's go!

52:17.110 --> 52:20.600
Follow me! Off we go!

52:20.780 --> 52:22.370
Run. Run. Run.

52:29.260 --> 52:30.350
Pepe?

52:41.970 --> 52:44.030
Where are you when I need you?

52:53.720 --> 52:55.950
Quit it!

52:56.120 --> 52:58.750
Peck on someone your own size.

52:58.920 --> 53:00.750
''Let's get into
the puppet business,'' you said.

53:00.920 --> 53:02.150
- I never--
- Shut up!

53:02.320 --> 53:04.320
- ''We'll be rich,'' you said.
- I didn't...

53:04.360 --> 53:07.260
Shut up. ''He's worth
a fortune,'' you said.

53:07.430 --> 53:08.990
Why do I always listen to you?

53:10.770 --> 53:11.760
Get off!

53:11.930 --> 53:12.990
Go away.

53:13.170 --> 53:14.160
Who do you suppose
that might be?

53:14.340 --> 53:16.630
Are you serious?

53:16.810 --> 53:18.430
Go away.

53:18.470 --> 53:19.600
Pinocchio!

53:35.090 --> 53:37.250
Out of my way.

54:14.000 --> 54:17.900
Let's put Lorenzini off
for just a few more minutes.

54:29.710 --> 54:31.840
Hey, I know you.

54:32.010 --> 54:33.740
You're friends with Lorenzini.

54:33.920 --> 54:35.580
We're finished with him now.

54:35.750 --> 54:37.720
- We're repugnant.
- Repentant.

54:37.890 --> 54:39.220
Yeah, that, too.

54:40.790 --> 54:44.120
And we're here to
ask for forgiveness.

54:44.290 --> 54:45.730
What's forgiveness?

54:45.890 --> 54:48.450
Forgiveness means that when
you did something really wrong,

54:48.630 --> 54:50.960
you want somebody to tell you...

54:51.130 --> 54:52.330
that it wasn't
really, really wrong,

54:52.500 --> 54:55.160
when you know what you did
was wrong because you did it!

54:57.710 --> 55:00.370
Please forgive me
for being a puppet,

55:00.540 --> 55:03.910
instead of a real boy
for my papa.

55:05.510 --> 55:07.350
I miss my daddy, too.

55:08.480 --> 55:10.310
You know,
it is possible...

55:10.490 --> 55:12.980
for you to become a real boy.

55:13.160 --> 55:14.880
How?

55:15.060 --> 55:16.680
All you need is a miracle.

55:16.860 --> 55:18.050
What's a miracle?

