Leaving?

01:23:20.510 --> 01:23:22.840
That would make me
a hypo-cricket.

01:23:23.010 --> 01:23:24.870
Union rules--
I'm with you forever.

01:23:25.050 --> 01:23:27.100
I just got to get some sleep.

01:23:32.250 --> 01:23:34.410
Papa! Pap, stop the cart.

01:23:34.590 --> 01:23:36.150
- What?
- Please stop the cart.

01:23:36.320 --> 01:23:37.650
There's just
one more little thing...

01:23:37.820 --> 01:23:39.550
I need to take care of.
It'll only take a minute.

01:23:44.330 --> 01:23:46.160
I'm not going
to sleep in no barn.

01:23:46.330 --> 01:23:47.800
Fine, then sleep
in the doghouse.

01:23:48.840 --> 01:23:50.130
Hello.

01:23:52.340 --> 01:23:55.100
Don't you answer back
when a person greets you?

01:23:55.280 --> 01:23:56.110
Hello.

01:23:56.280 --> 01:23:58.010
Haven't I seen you
somewhere before?

01:23:58.180 --> 01:24:01.940
No. Believe me,
l just got here.

01:24:02.120 --> 01:24:04.520
That sure isn't very much gold
you've got there.

01:24:04.750 --> 01:24:08.020
Excuse me, sonny. We're rich.

01:24:08.190 --> 01:24:09.680
That's not rich.

01:24:09.860 --> 01:24:11.450
This is rich.

01:24:13.560 --> 01:24:15.460
That's nothing but a rock.

01:24:15.630 --> 01:24:19.190
Yes, but if you take this road
five miles, there's a valley.

01:24:19.370 --> 01:24:20.360
I've been there.

01:24:20.530 --> 01:24:23.030
Drinking the water
turns bad boys into donkeys.

01:24:23.200 --> 01:24:24.260
Get out of here.

01:24:24.440 --> 01:24:26.840
Fine, then I won't
tell you about the gold.

01:24:27.010 --> 01:24:28.200
Gold?

01:24:28.380 --> 01:24:29.710
Keep this to yourselves.

01:24:29.880 --> 01:24:31.370
If you drink the water
while holding onto a rock...

01:24:31.550 --> 01:24:32.380
Yeah?

01:24:32.550 --> 01:24:33.570
It turns into gold.

01:24:33.750 --> 01:24:35.720
Gold?

01:24:35.880 --> 01:24:37.180
Would I lie?

01:24:39.090 --> 01:24:40.210
Bye.

01:24:44.420 --> 01:24:45.820
See you later, Papa.

01:24:45.990 --> 01:24:47.520
Pinocchio,
where are you going?

01:24:47.690 --> 01:24:49.220
To play with Lampwick.

01:24:49.400 --> 01:24:51.760
Did you do your studies
and all of your chores?

01:24:51.930 --> 01:24:53.190
Yes, Papa.

01:24:53.370 --> 01:24:56.060
Sometimes I wish
that nose still grew.

01:24:56.240 --> 01:24:57.360
Lampwick.

01:25:00.640 --> 01:25:02.700
Come on, Woody, let's go.

01:25:04.680 --> 01:25:06.040
Careful!

01:25:07.950 --> 01:25:09.510
We're--we're very sorry, sir.

01:25:09.680 --> 01:25:10.980
Yeah. Let us pick these up.

01:25:11.150 --> 01:25:15.710
- Don't you just hate that kid?
- Not as much as I hate you.

01:25:17.260 --> 01:25:18.250
Papa, Papa,

01:25:18.430 --> 01:25:20.220
I've got a great idea.

01:25:20.390 --> 01:25:23.450
How about carving me
a girlfriend?

01:25:23.630 --> 01:25:25.530
You've been a boy two minutes,

01:25:25.700 --> 01:25:27.360
already you're
thinking about girls?

01:25:27.530 --> 01:25:30.770
Am I going
to have trouble with you!

01:25:36.210 --> 01:25:37.900
And there you have it.

01:25:38.080 --> 01:25:42.240
Geppetto and Leona
lived happily ever after.

01:25:42.420 --> 01:25:44.470
Luigi ate a lot of socks,

01:25:44.650 --> 01:25:47.250
and all the donkeys
turned back into boys.

01:25:47.420 --> 01:25:49.010
It took some hard work.

01:25:49.190 --> 01:25:52.350
They had to do many good deeds
to earn the privilege.

01:25:52.530 --> 01:25:55.190
As for me,
l took a house on Lake Como...

01:25:55.360 --> 01:25:57.690
and played canasta
with a couple of locusts.

01:25:57.860 --> 01:25:59.730
So, ciao, my little saplings.
Arrivederci!

01:25:59.900 --> 01:26:02.700
And when you need me,
give me a holler.

01:26:02.870 --> 01:26:05.960
We'll see if we can
arrange something.
